data.description: Charming home and caring owners are looking for a new happy family for their lovingly maintained and upgraded home. Upgrades are numerous but include, windows throughout, siding (superior in looks and durability) New HVAC (both heat and AC) : 2020, New pool liner: 2020 and all new concrete around pool, new pool pump: 2023, water heater: 2018, dishwasher: 2018, concrete pad for camper or boat, 2017, fence reinforced with all new 4 x 4's; 2020 and power washed 2021. Remodeled kitchen with lots of storage. The stairs were moved to the dining room to a remodeled den to add natural light, recessed lighting in the family room, upgraded bathrooms, large yard with mature landscaping and yard, beautiful covered patio and salt water pool with many pool accessories conveying. New front door and storm door : 2020. This home has it all including 3 bedrooms upstairs with a full bath and an office downstairs with another full bath. Sheds and storage in the yard complete your dream home.
